91c0adef6503dc6d3c2c442170ef","tid":1862553,"uid":73143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"[全民三罷] 醫護工會並不代表所有 醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQoLAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQoLAS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWp8d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWp8d0.png&h=12ec3a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da5e1696222217b818e1587e0e17e6f2d3ef3081","tid":1862553,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"其實邊到話暫緩罷工？"},{"pid":"12a7352f02052c0d60d4d8b27a18cbd2e64014a6","tid":1862553,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"唔撚好返求下大家<br />\n港共就係要攻擊大家嘅軟弱位"}]}